<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='271000' id='t-271000'>Only girls are Secretary of State.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='273000' id='t-273000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:46
