</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 4:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='284000' id='t-284000'>PM: Because in her lifetime -- MA: That would be so.</span>
