</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:58
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>PM: Is that &quot;Girl 7?&quot; MA: Girl 7.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469000' id='t-469000'>And we lobbied</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471000' id='t-471000'>on behalf of women's issues.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='473000' id='t-473000'>So we managed to get two women judges</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='476000' id='t-476000'>on this war crimes tribunal.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='478000' id='t-478000'>And then what happened</span>
