<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='490000' id='t-490000'>PM: So when you look around the world</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='492000' id='t-492000'>and you see that, in many cases --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='494000' id='t-494000'>certainly in the Western world --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='496000' id='t-496000'>women are evolving into more leadership positions,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='499000' id='t-499000'>and even other places</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='501000' id='t-501000'>some barriers are being brought down,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='504000' id='t-504000'>but there's still so much violence,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='507000' id='t-507000'>still so many problems,</span>
