<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>and how the debts of countries work out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654000' id='t-654000'>So if you have women</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656000' id='t-656000'>in a variety of foreign policy posts,</span>
