<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='664000' id='t-664000'>PM: So how do we get</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='666000' id='t-666000'>this balance we're looking for, then, in the world?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='669000' id='t-669000'>More women's voices at the table?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='671000' id='t-671000'>More men who believe</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='673000' id='t-673000'>that the balance is best?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:26
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='675000' id='t-675000'>MA: Well I think one of the things --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677000' id='t-677000'>I'm chairman of the board of an organization</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='679000' id='t-679000'>called the National Democratic Institute</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='681000' id='t-681000'>that works to support women candidates.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='684000' id='t-684000'>I think that we need</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686000' id='t-686000'>to help in other countries</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='688000' id='t-688000'>to train women</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='690000' id='t-690000'>to be in political office,</span>
