<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694000' id='t-694000'>develop political voices.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='696000' id='t-696000'>I think we also need to be supportive</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='699000' id='t-699000'>when businesses are being created</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='702000' id='t-702000'>and just make sure that women help each other.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='704000' id='t-704000'>Now I have a saying</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706000' id='t-706000'>that I feel very strongly about,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708000' id='t-708000'>because I am of a certain age</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710000' id='t-710000'>where, when I started in my career,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='712000' id='t-712000'>believe it or not, there were other women who criticized me:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='715000' id='t-715000'>&quot;Why aren't you in the carpool line?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='718000' id='t-718000'>or &quot;Aren't your children suffering</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='720000' id='t-720000'>because you're not there all the time?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='722000' id='t-722000'>And I think we have a tendency to make each other feel guilty.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='725000' id='t-725000'>In fact, I think &quot;guilt&quot; is every woman's middle name.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='729000' id='t-729000'>And so I think what needs to happen</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='731000' id='t-731000'>is we need to help each other.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='734000' id='t-734000'>And my motto is that there's a special place in hell</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='736000' id='t-736000'>for women who don't help each other.</span>
</span>
</p>
