</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:38
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='747000' id='t-747000'>PM: Well Secretary Albright, I guess you'll be going to heaven.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='751000' id='t-751000'>Thank you for joining us today.</span>
